@startuml 过程视图-覆盖率可视化流程

actor "用户" as User
control "前端系统" as Frontend
control "后端系统" as Backend
database "数据库" as Database
boundary "静态文件系统" as Static

' 用户请求查看覆盖率数据
User -> Frontend: 请求查看覆盖率数据
activate User
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend: 调用接口获取覆盖率数据
activate Backend
Backend -> Database: 查询覆盖率数据
activate Database
Database --> Backend: 返回覆盖率数据
deactivate Database
Backend --> Frontend: 返回覆盖率数据
deactivate Backend

Frontend -> Frontend: 构造表格和柱状图，生成告警信息
Frontend --> User: 展示覆盖率数据
deactivate Frontend

' 用户请求查看覆盖率报告
User -> Frontend: 请求查看覆盖率报告
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Frontend: 构造覆盖率报告的 URL
Frontend -> Static: 通过 URL 请求覆盖率报告
activate Static
Static --> Frontend: 返回覆盖率报告
deactivate Static
Frontend --> User: 展示覆盖率报告
deactivate Frontend
deactivate User

@enduml
